# 🌦️ Weather Report - Power BI Dashboard

This repository contains a **Power BI report (`weather_report.pbix`)** that provides insights into weather conditions and air quality levels.

## 📌 Features
- Interactive dashboard built in Power BI.
- Air Quality Index (AQI) visualization with **color-coded categories**:
  - Good (Green)
  - Moderate (Yellow)
  - Poor (Orange)
  - Unhealthy (Red)
  - Severe (Purple)
  - Hazardous (Dark Maroon)
- Weather trend analysis (temperature, humidity, PM10).
- Dynamic filtering for exploring different time ranges.

## 🚀 Usage
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/<Nihalakshay2004>/Weather-Report-PowerBI.git
